            Observaciones Técnicas
        &lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;div style="background: white; padding: 16px 18px; border-left: 3px solid #7ED321; color: #212121; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 13px;"&gt;
            Sin descripción técnica disponible.
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- FOOTER --&gt;
    &lt;div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7ED321 0%, #5CB800 100%); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 12px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.6px;"&gt;
        4PTelecom - CONAGUA
    &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
